prompts.text:
Import this product and push it to ${arguments.store_name} as a draft:
${arguments.product_url}

Steps: 1) dsers_store_discover. 2) dsers_product_import. 3) Show preview. 4) dsers_store_push with visibility_mode=backend_only.

Bulk import these products with a ${arguments.price_multiplier}x price markup and push to ${arguments.store_name}:
${arguments.product_urls}

Steps: 1) dsers_store_discover. 2) dsers_product_import with rules. 3) Show previews. 4) dsers_store_push for each.

Import this product and push it to ALL my stores:
${arguments.product_url}

Steps: 1) dsers_store_discover — list all stores. 2) dsers_product_import. 3) dsers_store_push with all stores.

Import this product and optimize for SEO before pushing to ${arguments.store_name}:
${arguments.product_url}
Target audience: ${arguments.target_audience}

Workflow: 1) dsers_store_discover. 2) dsers_product_import — get raw preview. 3) Rewrite title and description for SEO. 4) Re-import with rules. 5) Show preview for approval. 6) dsers_store_push.
